{"tid":1906912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗興舔聖門 估計有萬八宗病例","createTime":"2020-03-02T09:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T07:26:54.000Z","uid":72009,"like":249,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"ce41cbd43c9a043764955fea7104444bd5316ff0","tid":1906912,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）向全球擴散，伊朗是中國境外最多死亡病例的國家，國際專家對伊朗疫情規模持懷疑態度，認為實際情況恐怕比官方公佈的要嚴重許多。伊朗當局一直被指防疫不力，政府雖然實行停課及關閉體育館，又呼籲民眾避免前往公共地方，但宗教領袖一直拒絕關閉聖地，包括聖城兼疫區庫姆（Qom）仍然有信徒朝聖，並維持傳統舔聖地的一道聖門，衞生及防疫意識極低。<br />\n<br />\n截至周日為止伊朗官方公佈共有978人確診及54人死亡，但非官方數字相信更加高。英國廣播公司波斯語頻道（BBC Persian）早前指武漢肺炎已在伊朗奪走210條人命，伊朗政府強烈否認；伊朗流亡組織「人民聖戰組織」（People's Mujahedin）則聲稱，國內死亡病例已「突破300」，確診數則高達1.5萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n國際專家也認為伊朗的情況實際上更加嚴重，6名加拿大流行病學家使用數學模型估計，伊朗境內約有1.8萬宗病例，但估算將源自伊朗的其他國家病例也納入其中。研究作者之一、多倫多大學傳染病專家戈查（Isaac Bogoch）說：「當一個國家的疫情蔓延到其他地區時，這個國家的感染負擔恐怕是相當沉重。」<br />\n<br />\n「無國界記者組織」（Reporters Without Borders）上周批評德黑蘭當局處理疫情的方式，指控伊朗政府扼殺有關疫情擴散的新聞。官方數據顯示，伊朗武漢肺炎死亡率超過5.5%，遠高於其他國家。中國死亡率為3.5%，疫情同樣相當嚴重的意大利則為2%。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗自前年被美國實施嚴厲制裁後，當局正致力應付經濟危機，導致國內疫情加劇。法國國際關係暨戰略研究院（French Institute for International and Strategic Affairs）伊朗分析員科維爾（Thierry Coville）說：「為何伊朗不讓班機停飛中國？有個合理的解釋是，中國是最後一批購買伊朗石油的國家之一。他們必須（與中國）維持經濟關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200302/HBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200302%2FHBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE%2F&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=d1b73a37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200302%2FHBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE%2F&h=75871d1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200302/HBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200302/large/1583121165_588a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583121165_588a.jpg&h=1615c3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dd7490fe296c83d901dd2a6f0f9f72a3a6d77f","tid":1906912,"uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f972e2ba910082797c1da24e7dfa6d9451676f","tid":1906912,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20b08fac3476b4943e3a44c148b062ebed0e542","tid":1906912,"uid":4942,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dc9116203e4872e6e58fcc68ea2a3921da9e9c","tid":1906912,"uid":201604,"like":134,"dislike":7,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"我都想舔靚女聖門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1720b8b2266df97b2fef266c577618a2d07d33","tid":1906912,"uid":269680,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因支而發達 因支而滅亡 <br />\n真實事例<br />\n不錯不錯"},{"pid":"8637efcb0b0ca80e313fd36c0b30edc953bf907f","tid":1906912,"uid":195995,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"舔完聖門就上去見真主<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e2b9230bd7007d5523ecaececac1fd5237108d","tid":1906912,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42ab175fb960b5e8986f4003bfb593de349b79e","tid":1906912,"uid":83713,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"點解班專家懷疑伊朗但就信哂支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw伊朗真係自作孽"},{"pid":"8ce95f8d1e047ec2e096d022425fd52d92e8bc48","tid":1906912,"uid":1886,"like":148,"dislike":7,"score":141,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiZZOTX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiZZOTX.png&h=753eaa2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b913dedc19514824d2a2c7958c45a656ee728db2","tid":1906912,"uid":8014,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"果然真係natural selection <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n低鳩能民族抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b39dcb264a9884c5d8e6f3699b99208131c8c5","tid":1906912,"uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"如有波斯聖女小門，大家奶唔奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fbec862517b87b941bfef285dab83ab5ce0f7f","tid":1906912,"uid":8014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"f42ab175fb960b5e8986f4003bfb593de349b79e","tid":1906912,"uid":83713,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"點解班專家懷疑伊朗但就信哂支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw伊朗真係自作孽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:15:05.000Z","msg