\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583121165_588a.jpg&h=1615c3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"其他伊斯蘭國家呢？"},{"pid":"20113a162a1b72acd463a1fa5d5b467ec75f33b2","tid":1906912,"uid":336922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"佢 lam完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二個又lam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人教佢地D口水有細菌又有病毒既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1cf0e3e8d5687c9cfb02edd4abe3c484cd20f8","tid":1906912,"uid":38946,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:55:32.000Z","msg":"連登從此多個動詞&quot;舔聖門&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a28ed7666730032740f039e81ad2ffec267301d","tid":1906912,"uid":138609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"美國都未攻打伊朗<br />\n伊朗就自作孽自爆埋<br />\n侵侵實笑到見牙唔見眼<br />\n賠了夫人又折兵 呢個就係親支那下場"},{"pid":"37d103d8ace358800f097237d7dfc3e2b7865a95","tid":1906912,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f7b5a7cc1b9526cb50bdea444d5112a0090ee7","tid":1906912,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:59:00.000Z","msg":"奶閪都無咁毒"},{"pid":"5da5c38e