689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce41cbd43c9a043764955fea7104444bd5316ff0","tid":1906912,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）向全球擴散，伊朗是中國境外最多死亡病例的國家，國際專家對伊朗疫情規模持懷疑態度，認為實際情況恐怕比官方公佈的要嚴重許多。伊朗當局一直被指防疫不力，政府雖然實行停課及關閉體育館，又呼籲民眾避免前往公共地方，但宗教領袖一直拒絕關閉聖地，包括聖城兼疫區庫姆（Qom）仍然有信徒朝聖，並維持傳統舔聖地的一道聖門，衞生及防疫意識極低。<br />\n<br />\n截至周日為止伊朗官方公佈共有978人確診及54人死亡，但非官方數字相信更加高。英國廣播公司波斯語頻道（BBC Persian）早前指武漢肺炎已在伊朗奪走210條人命，伊朗政府強烈否認；伊朗流亡組織「人民聖戰組織」（People's Mujahedin）則聲稱，國內死亡病例已「突破300」，確診數則高達1.5萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n國際專家也認為伊朗的情況實際上更加嚴重，6名加拿大流行病學家使用數學模型估計，伊朗境內約有1.8萬宗病例，但估算將源自伊朗的其他國家病例也納入其中。研究作者之一、多倫多大學傳染病專家戈查（Isaac Bogoch）說：「當一個國家的疫情蔓延到其他地區時，這個國家的感染負擔恐怕是相當沉重。」<br />\n<br />\n「無國界記者組織」（Reporters Without Borders）上周批評德黑蘭當局處理疫情的方式，指控伊朗政府扼殺有關疫情擴散的新聞。官方數據顯示，伊朗武漢肺炎死亡率超過5.5%，遠高於其他國家。中國死亡率為3.5%，疫情同樣相當嚴重的意大利則為2%。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗自前年被美國實施嚴厲制裁後，當局正致力應付經濟危機，導致國內疫情加劇。法國國際關係暨戰略研究院（French Institute for International and Strategic Affairs）伊朗分析員科維爾（Thierry Coville）說：「為何伊朗不讓班機停飛中國？有個合理的解釋是，中國是最後一批購買伊朗石油的國家之一。他們必須（與中國）維持經濟關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200302/HBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200302%2FHBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE%2F&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=d1b73a37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200302%2FHBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE%2F&h=75871d1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200302/HBXOMCZ243YAQTCFS7B7LO4ARE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200302/large/1583121165_588a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200302%2Flarge%2F1583121165_588a.jpg&h=1615c3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77367e5cbd19a5f57874c28b8eb601106cf5a6e2","tid":1906912,"uid":36563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ce95f8d1e047ec2e096d022425fd52d92e8bc48","tid":1906912,"uid":1886,"like":148,"dislike":7,"score":141,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jiZZOTX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjiZZOTX.png&h=753eaa2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c891539bf3d32bb2e760ba72871f024fd1be3b5","tid":1906912,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17043278e8aca7fe37679fd59123df71f88f52c6","tid":1906912,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23bbea20394897f51d7181c03f67ce41466c5b4","tid":1906912,"uid":17379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"係咪佢地宗教習慣用手攞食野所以傳得特別快<br />\n<br />\n利申：我無知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"佢地打招呼要攬攬錫錫"},{"pid":"80956462f1f4c88c05dbef7b91896abaac29f237","tid":1906912,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a894ba34cddaf6af0724cc4c189f6bfd88b48f1","tid":1906912,"uid":290741,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"43b39dcb264a9884c5d8e6f3699b99208131c8c5","tid":1906912,"uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"如有波斯聖女小門，大家奶唔奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"repl